<p>At TradeManagementApp, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website and use our services.</p>

<h3>Information Collection</h3>
<p>We collect information that you voluntarily provide to us, including personal details such as name, email address, and documents you upload. We may also collect information automatically, such as your IP address, browser type, and operating system when you visit our website.</p>

